      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine find! This vehicle is in showroom condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it rolled off the lot. It has been meticulously maintained with not a single detail overlooked, offering a truly 'like-new' experience for its next owner. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one!",
